From ec7ce2fba1638d6b488d78b9539b9abf8a492b6f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "v.oleynikov" <vasily.oleynikov@flant.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 14:10:50 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Scope startup CRD lookup to LINSTOR's own CRD

getDbVersion() listed every CustomResourceDefinition in the cluster and
deserialized each full OpenAPI schema only to find the linstorversion CRD.
Non-standard schema extensions added by other operators (e.g. Deckhouse's
x-kubernetes-sensitive-data) are unknown to the bundled fabric8 model and
raise UnrecognizedPropertyException, aborting controller startup with a
spurious database initialization error (exit 20).

Use a metadata.name field selector so the API server returns only the
linstorversion CRD; foreign CRDs are never fetched or deserialized.

Signed-off-by: v.oleynikov <vasily.oleynikov@flant.com>
---
 .../transaction/ControllerK8sCrdTransactionMgr.java    | 10 +++++++++-
 1 file changed, 9 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/controller/src/main/java/com/linbit/linstor/transaction/ControllerK8sCrdTransactionMgr.java b/controller/src/main/java/com/linbit/linstor/transaction/ControllerK8sCrdTransactionMgr.java
index e2b1e1b..77623c6 100644
--- a/controller/src/main/java/com/linbit/linstor/transaction/ControllerK8sCrdTransactionMgr.java
+++ b/controller/src/main/java/com/linbit/linstor/transaction/ControllerK8sCrdTransactionMgr.java
@@ -104,8 +104,16 @@ public class ControllerK8sCrdTransactionMgr implements TransactionMgrK8sCrd
     public Integer getDbVersion()
     {
         Integer ret = null;
+        // Restrict the CRD list to LINSTOR's own linstorversion CRD via a metadata.name field
+        // selector. Listing all CRDs would deserialize every CRD schema in the cluster, which
+        // fails on non-standard OpenAPI extensions added by other operators (e.g. Deckhouse sets
+        // x-kubernetes-sensitive-data), unknown to the bundled fabric8 model, and would abort the
+        // controller startup with a spurious database initialization error.
         CustomResourceDefinitionList list = k8sClient.apiextensions().v1().customResourceDefinitions()
-            .list(new ListOptionsBuilder().build());
+            .list(new ListOptionsBuilder()
+                .withFieldSelector("metadata.name="
+                    + LinstorVersionCrd.LINSTOR_CRD_NAME + "." + LinstorVersionCrd.GROUP)
+                .build());
         if (!list.getItems().isEmpty())
         {
             for (CustomResourceDefinition crd : list.getItems())
